<Base
  title="How to Verify an Email Address Without Sending an Email"
  description="You can verify an email without sending anything: syntax check, MX record lookup, then an SMTP handshake that asks the server whether the mailbox exists and disconnects before sending. How each step works."
  schema={schema}
